# Design System & Styling

## Color (Strict Monochrome)
Dilarang aksen non-monochrome di luar daftar ini.

| Token | Hex | Tailwind |
|-------|-----|----------|
| Primary Black | `#000000` | `bg-black`, `text-black` |
| Secondary Dark | `#1A1A1A` | `bg-[#1a1a1a]` |
| Body Gray | `#333333` | `text-[#333333]` |
| Disabled | `#999999` | `text-[#999999]` |
| Light BG | `#F5F5F5` | `bg-[#f5f5f5]` |
| White | `#FFFFFF` | `bg-white`, `text-white` |

Semantic (status only): Success `#22C55E`, Error `#EF4444`, Warning `#F59E0B`

## Typography (Montserrat)
- Logo: 900, uppercase, tracking-wider
- H1: 800, uppercase, `tracking-[0.15em]`, `text-4xl md:text-7xl`
- H2: 700, uppercase, `text-3xl md:text-5xl`
- H3: 700, uppercase, `text-2xl md:text-3xl`
- Body: 400, `leading-relaxed`
- Buttons: 700, uppercase, `tracking-[0.2em]`
- Prices: 700, tracking-tight

## Layout
- Grid 12 kolom desktop; container `max-w-7xl`, `px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-16`
- Spacing: kelipatan 8px (`p-2`, `p-4`, `p-6`, `p-8`, `p-12`, `p-16`)
- Product images: ratio 3:4, `object-cover`; banners: 16:9 atau `h-screen`

## Components
- **Primary button**: bg black, text white, `rounded-none`, `py-4 px-10`; hover invert (white bg, black border 2px, black text)
- **Secondary button**: border 2px black, transparent; hover fill black + white text
- **Inputs**: underlined only — `border-b border-[#e0e0e0] border-t-0 border-x-0 bg-transparent rounded-none focus:border-black`
- **Badges**: black bg/white text or thin black border, uppercase, `rounded-none`

## Animation
- Framer Motion untuk micro-interactions
- Hover: `transition-all duration-300 ease-out`
- Page: fade-in + subtle slide up; list grids: stagger 50–100ms
